First Department,

October, 1947.

(October 3, 1947.) In the Matter of the Arbitration between M. Hausman & Son, Inc., Appellant, and Max Drucker, Doing Business under the Name of Max Drucker Silk Co., Respondent.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements. No opinion. Present — Peek, P. J., Glennon, Dore, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.
